Investor Relations


 


First Level Entertainment Group, Inc. is a development stage company. First Level is the parent company of VIP WINK CORP, MESSAGE ATTIC CORP. and MOBILE SONARS INC. It also owns intellectual property, collectively entitled I Love Kids, which consists of thirty five original songs recorded with nearly two hundred original children’s names inserted in the songs.

            First Level Entertainment Group, Inc.’s corporate office is located in Parkland, Florida. As a public, non- trading, company First Level submits financial statements to the U.S. Security and Exchange Commission. These statements disclose information about the Company’s financial position.

            A complete listing of the Company’s financial statements and other public filings with the SEC may be found by clicking on the links below:

          • Click Here for Company Information
For additional information call us at 855-847-9465 or reach us through our contact page.















 


  






