First Level Entertainment Group, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 1:45 PM ET
Software

Company Overview of First Level Entertainment Group, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
First Level Entertainment Group, Inc. operates in the entertainment business in the United States. The company focuses on developing mobile applications. Its products include VIPwink, a mobile application that enables individuals, brands, and others with a Twitter following to differentiate and monetize their fans and followers; and MobileSonars, a white label mobile application, which allows a partner site to monetize and offer deals, discounts, and coupons to a database of users that are on property or at the event in real time. The company was formerly known as Sound Kitchen Entertainment Group, Inc. and changed its name to First Level Entertainment Group, Inc. in August 2011. First Level...
First Level Entertainment Group, Inc. operates in the entertainment business in the United States. The company focuses on developing mobile applications. Its products include VIPwink, a mobile application that enables individuals, brands, and others with a Twitter following to differentiate and monetize their fans and followers; and MobileSonars, a white label mobile application, which allows a partner site to monetize and offer deals, discounts, and coupons to a database of users that are on property or at the event in real time. The company was formerly known as Sound Kitchen Entertainment Group, Inc. and changed its name to First Level Entertainment Group, Inc. in August 2011. First Level Entertainment Group, Inc. was founded in 2008 and is based in Fort Lauderdale, Florida.
Detailed Description


