Warner Bros. Entertainment Inc. (colloquially known as Warner Bros. and Warner Bros. Pictures and for a time trading as Warner Brothers Pictures, Inc.[7]) is an American entertainment company that is a division of Time Warner and is headquartered in Burbank, California. It is one of the "Big Six" major American film studios.
Warner Bros. is a member of the Motion Picture Association of America (MPAA).



